WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 14=

00:01:38.210 --> 00:01:39.490 line:80%
Thank you very much.

00:01:40.090 --> 00:01:41.060 line:80%
Miss Feng.

00:01:41.340 --> 00:01:42.180 line:80%
Mr. Dai.

00:01:43.700 --> 00:01:44.650 line:80%
Miss Feng.

00:01:48.540 --> 00:01:50.130 line:80%
- Village Chief.
- Miss Feng.

00:01:50.130 --> 00:01:51.262 line:80%
Thank you, Miss Feng.

00:01:51.273 --> 00:01:52.490 line:80%
It's a relief you're unharmed.

00:01:52.490 --> 00:01:53.340 line:80%
Village Chief,

00:01:53.340 --> 00:01:55.010 line:80%
weren't you told to hide first?

00:01:55.010 --> 00:01:55.909 line:80%
The Village Chief said

00:01:56.130 --> 00:01:58.570 line:80%
he wouldn't be at ease
until he saw you safe.

00:01:58.570 --> 00:02:00.090 line:80%
Luckily, we made it in time.

00:02:00.090 --> 00:02:01.490 line:80%
Did they make things hard for you?

00:02:02.090 --> 00:02:03.010 line:80%
No, no.

00:02:03.010 --> 00:02:04.700 line:80%
They just locked me up.

00:02:04.700 --> 00:02:05.570 line:80%
I got lucky.

00:02:05.570 --> 00:02:06.790 line:80%
I found a hidden passage

00:02:07.210 --> 00:02:08.810 line:80%
and ran out to meet up with Qingyun.

00:02:09.140 --> 00:02:11.210 line:80%
How fortunate you are.

00:02:11.780 --> 00:02:13.300 line:80%
Many thanks to you both.

00:02:14.210 --> 00:02:15.050 line:80%
Otherwise,

00:02:15.370 --> 00:02:17.860 line:80%
who knows what would've happened?

00:02:18.020 --> 00:02:19.370 line:80%
We've always lived here

00:02:19.370 --> 00:02:22.180 line:80%
by the rules and kept the sect laws.

00:02:22.180 --> 00:02:25.410 line:80%
I truly don't know why they arrested us.

00:02:25.410 --> 00:02:27.740 line:80%
Even if Xing did something wrong,

00:02:27.740 --> 00:02:30.140 line:80%
they shouldn't have taken
the whole village.

00:02:30.410 --> 00:02:32.060 line:80%
Why would they seize the villagers?

00:02:32.530 --> 00:02:34.140 line:80%
We're sect members after all.

00:02:35.090 --> 00:02:36.220 line:80%
One of their own.

00:02:36.790 --> 00:02:38.050 line:80%
They're making corpse slaves.

00:02:38.530 --> 00:02:39.710 line:80%
Corpse slaves?

00:02:40.300 --> 00:02:41.300 line:80%
What are those?

00:02:41.900 --> 00:02:43.410 line:80%
Corpse slaves...

00:02:45.690 --> 00:02:46.530 line:80%
Village Chief,

00:02:46.900 --> 00:02:47.900 line:80%
you've seen them before?

00:02:49.690 --> 00:02:50.860 line:80%
Nineteen years ago,

00:02:51.460 --> 00:02:53.490 line:80%
when the former chief,

00:02:53.490 --> 00:02:55.460 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng, was still alive,

00:02:55.460 --> 00:02:56.530 line:80%
my eldest nephew

00:02:56.530 --> 00:02:59.410 line:80%
was taken and made into a corpse slave.

00:02:59.410 --> 00:03:01.300 line:80%
He died on the Youming Path.

00:03:01.900 --> 00:03:03.460 line:80%
Those turned into corpse slaves

00:03:03.460 --> 00:03:05.780 line:80%
lose all reason
and are controlled by others,

00:03:05.780 --> 00:03:09.300 line:80%
and in the end, their bodies rot away.

00:03:09.970 --> 00:03:11.410 line:80%
After the Battle of Mount Tu,

00:03:11.970 --> 00:03:14.740 line:80%
I thought the nightmare
was finally over.

00:03:15.060 --> 00:03:15.900 line:80%
Yet they've

00:03:16.860 --> 00:03:18.890 line:80%
started again.

00:03:19.340 --> 00:03:20.180 line:80%
Xiaohan,

00:03:20.490 --> 00:03:21.340 line:80%
we must return at once

00:03:21.340 --> 00:03:22.180 line:80%
and report this

00:03:23.060 --> 00:03:23.900 line:80%
to Master.

00:03:24.090 --> 00:03:25.530 line:80%
I fear that before we can report it,

00:03:25.530 --> 00:03:27.740 line:80%
the villagers will be fully refined.

00:03:28.300 --> 00:03:30.930 line:80%
By then, the Hanhai Mountains

00:03:30.930 --> 00:03:33.250 line:80%
and Jianghu will face disaster.

00:03:34.300 --> 00:03:35.140 line:80%
The priority now

00:03:36.940 --> 00:03:38.180 line:80%
is to stop them from continuing

00:03:38.180 --> 00:03:39.810 line:80%
to make corpse slaves.

00:03:42.900 --> 00:03:44.180 line:80%
I know a place

00:03:44.530 --> 00:03:45.620 line:80%
that might

00:03:45.620 --> 00:03:47.340 line:80%
hold a way to stop them.

00:03:49.900 --> 00:03:53.540 line:80%
(Li Sect, Jiuzhou Archive,
Treasured Tomes)

00:04:02.340 --> 00:04:03.180 line:80%
Come.

00:04:09.060 --> 00:04:10.580 line:80%
When I was young,

00:04:10.580 --> 00:04:11.970 line:80%
I once came here to clean.

00:04:12.300 --> 00:04:13.180 line:80%
I heard

00:04:13.490 --> 00:04:15.580 line:80%
this place holds books and records

00:04:15.580 --> 00:04:17.580 line:80%
collected by generations of chiefs.

00:04:18.500 --> 00:04:20.530 line:80%
The former chief disliked reading

00:04:21.090 --> 00:04:22.730 line:80%
and locked this place away.

00:04:23.410 --> 00:04:24.410 line:80%
After his death,

00:04:24.900 --> 00:04:26.780 line:80%
no one remembered it anymore.

00:04:27.090 --> 00:04:29.170 line:80%
I'll look for any texts
that mention corpse slaves.

00:04:36.500 --> 00:04:38.300 line:80%
(Jiuzhou Archive)

00:04:39.210 --> 00:04:40.970 line:80%
Jiuzhou Archive?

00:04:40.970 --> 00:04:41.810 line:80%
Miss Feng,

00:04:42.340 --> 00:04:43.580 line:80%
you've heard of it too?

00:04:44.410 --> 00:04:47.650 line:80%
I once heard a friend mention it.

00:04:47.650 --> 00:04:48.820 line:80%
Was this friend of yours

00:04:48.820 --> 00:04:51.380 line:80%
someone of high standing in the sect?

00:04:51.380 --> 00:04:52.460 line:80%
I only know

00:04:52.460 --> 00:04:54.900 line:80%
he read some books in Jiuzhou Archive

00:04:55.700 --> 00:04:58.500 line:80%
and even found a dragon beast scale.

00:04:58.780 --> 00:05:01.650 line:80%
Your friend must be the Mu kid.

00:05:09.980 --> 00:05:12.140 line:80%
(Yan Xu, Elder Zhibi of Li Sect)

00:05:13.580 --> 00:05:14.610 line:80%
Elder Yan.

00:05:18.500 --> 00:05:19.340 line:80%
Elder Yan,

00:05:19.820 --> 00:05:21.170 line:80%
you're still alive?

00:05:21.460 --> 00:05:22.300 line:80%
Gui,

00:05:23.610 --> 00:05:25.090 line:80%
we haven't met in over ten years,

00:05:25.090 --> 00:05:27.003 line:80%
and the first thing you do
is curse me to death?

00:05:29.050 --> 00:05:29.890 line:80%
Village Chief,

00:05:30.940 --> 00:05:31.820 line:80%
you know him?

00:05:32.340 --> 00:05:34.700 line:80%
This is Elder Zhibi of Li Sect.

00:05:34.700 --> 00:05:35.900 line:80%
Elder Yan,

00:05:35.900 --> 00:05:38.210 line:80%
who specializes
in recording sect history.

00:05:38.210 --> 00:05:40.650 line:80%
I hadn't heard from you for years.

00:05:40.650 --> 00:05:43.210 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng died suddenly

00:05:43.210 --> 00:05:44.780 line:80%
and named no successor.

00:05:44.780 --> 00:05:46.210 line:80%
Nie Zhe took the position improperly,

00:05:46.210 --> 00:05:47.940 line:80%
so he locked me here,

00:05:47.940 --> 00:05:50.140 line:80%
trying to force me
to alter sect history.

00:05:50.850 --> 00:05:53.940 line:80%
A year ago, Mu Qingyan

00:05:53.940 --> 00:05:56.460 line:80%
was gravely injured by Nie Zhe.

00:05:56.460 --> 00:05:58.460 line:80%
Luckily, he hid here.

00:05:58.460 --> 00:06:00.380 line:80%
I saved his life.

00:06:01.580 --> 00:06:04.650 line:80%
With his aloof and unruly nature,

00:06:04.650 --> 00:06:06.900 line:80%
he'd even have friends?

00:06:08.050 --> 00:06:08.890 line:80%
Who are you?

00:06:09.140 --> 00:06:10.530 line:80%
How did you meet him?

00:06:11.380 --> 00:06:12.580 line:80%
After he escaped from here,

00:06:13.380 --> 00:06:15.290 line:80%
he reached Qingzhu Gang to recover.

00:06:15.780 --> 00:06:17.850 line:80%
We learned he was in danger this time,

00:06:18.500 --> 00:06:19.700 line:80%
so we came to help.

00:06:20.340 --> 00:06:22.530 line:80%
No wonder you were going
to Qinglong Altar.

00:06:22.530 --> 00:06:23.370 line:80%
Elder Yan,

00:06:24.050 --> 00:06:25.530 line:80%
you must have examined

00:06:25.530 --> 00:06:26.820 line:80%
all the books here.

00:06:27.210 --> 00:06:28.050 line:80%
Do you know

00:06:28.410 --> 00:06:29.500 line:80%
a cure for corpse slaves?

00:06:30.780 --> 00:06:32.140 line:80%
Corpse slaves?

00:06:33.380 --> 00:06:34.730 line:80%
Didn't they disappear long ago?

00:06:34.730 --> 00:06:36.500 line:80%
Nie Zhe has started refining them again.

00:06:36.500 --> 00:06:37.340 line:80%
I suppose

00:06:37.730 --> 00:06:39.610 line:80%
he means to use them against Mu Qingyan.

00:06:41.140 --> 00:06:42.580 line:80%
That scoundrel Nie Zhe

00:06:43.290 --> 00:06:44.940 line:80%
is becoming
more and more like his uncle.

00:06:44.940 --> 00:06:46.780 line:80%
Ignorant, reckless, and tyrannical.

00:06:48.530 --> 00:06:50.530 line:80%
Let's talk about corpse slaves first.

00:06:51.460 --> 00:06:52.820 line:80%
The records say

00:06:53.290 --> 00:06:54.460 line:80%
corpse slaves are refined

00:06:54.460 --> 00:06:57.420 line:80%
using Gu worms
and Shanci Mushroom poison.

00:06:57.700 --> 00:07:01.380 line:80%
As long as we find herbs
that counter the poison,

00:07:01.380 --> 00:07:04.500 line:80%
we can temporarily suppress
their toxicity.

00:07:05.290 --> 00:07:07.510 line:80%
But I don't know

00:07:07.940 --> 00:07:09.650 line:80%
how to completely remove it.

00:07:11.610 --> 00:07:13.380 line:80%
All things restrain one another.

00:07:13.380 --> 00:07:15.730 line:80%
If we find where Shanci Mushrooms grow,

00:07:15.730 --> 00:07:17.290 line:80%
we'll surely find what counters them.

00:07:17.730 --> 00:07:18.940 line:80%
I know where they grow.

00:07:19.380 --> 00:07:20.220 line:80%
I'll go.

00:07:20.340 --> 00:07:21.180 line:80%
We'll go together.

00:07:33.140 --> 00:07:34.290 line:80%
Why are there so many people?

00:07:34.433 --> 00:07:35.806 line:80%
The EightClaw Prison was destroyed.

00:07:36.170 --> 00:07:37.290 line:80%
To restart the refining pool,

00:07:37.606 --> 00:07:39.412 line:80%
they'll need a large amount
of the mushrooms.

00:07:40.500 --> 00:07:42.286 line:80%
Xiaohan, take care
of the three on the right.

00:07:43.380 --> 00:07:44.220 line:80%
Two.

00:07:44.530 --> 00:07:45.370 line:80%
I'll handle the rest.

00:07:51.730 --> 00:07:52.710 line:80%
The summons has sounded.

00:07:52.970 --> 00:07:53.970 line:80%
Hurry to assemble. Go.

00:07:53.970 --> 00:07:55.090 line:80%
The summons of Li Sect.

00:07:55.460 --> 00:07:57.650 line:80%
Something must've happened
near Xuanwu Altar.

00:07:58.460 --> 00:07:59.530 line:80%
Could it be Mu Qingyan?

00:08:00.016 --> 00:08:01.449 line:80%
Has he begun attacking Xuanwu Altar?

00:08:02.410 --> 00:08:03.530 line:80%
They're using corpse slaves

00:08:03.530 --> 00:08:04.380 line:80%
to deal with him.

00:08:05.390 --> 00:08:06.510 line:80%
Hurry and find the antidote.

00:08:07.860 --> 00:08:12.820 line:80%
(Li Sect, Xuanwu Altar)

00:08:15.650 --> 00:08:16.700 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:08:16.970 --> 00:08:18.020 line:80%
over a year ago,

00:08:18.380 --> 00:08:19.610 line:80%
you fled in disgrace.

00:08:19.900 --> 00:08:21.650 line:80%
Everyone thought you were dead.

00:08:22.050 --> 00:08:23.290 line:80%
The Chief was merciful

00:08:23.780 --> 00:08:26.170 line:80%
and even set up a cenotaph for you.

00:08:26.700 --> 00:08:28.580 line:80%
You feel no gratitude for his kindness,

00:08:28.900 --> 00:08:30.500 line:80%
yet you turn on us instead?

00:08:31.380 --> 00:08:32.330 line:80%
Li Sect

00:08:32.650 --> 00:08:34.410 line:80%
belongs to the Mu clan to begin with.

00:08:34.690 --> 00:08:35.930 line:80%
Anyone with sense

00:08:36.450 --> 00:08:37.650 line:80%
wouldn't stop the Young Master.

00:08:37.650 --> 00:08:38.650 line:80%
Shut up, You Guanyue.

00:08:38.900 --> 00:08:40.410 line:80%
Is this your place to speak?

00:08:40.620 --> 00:08:42.050 line:80%
You rose by slick words

00:08:42.050 --> 00:08:43.620 line:80%
and shameless flattery.

00:08:43.620 --> 00:08:44.690 line:80%
Look around.

00:08:44.690 --> 00:08:46.170 line:80%
Who here truly respects you?

00:08:46.170 --> 00:08:47.010 line:80%
You...

00:08:49.410 --> 00:08:50.290 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:08:50.290 --> 00:08:52.100 line:80%
with the strategist here today,

00:08:52.100 --> 00:08:53.780 line:80%
prepare to die.

00:08:53.780 --> 00:08:54.980 line:80%
This time,

00:08:54.980 --> 00:08:57.050 line:80%
you won't even get a cenotaph.

00:08:57.050 --> 00:08:58.050 line:80%
Enough talk.

00:08:58.050 --> 00:08:58.910 line:80%
Young Master,

00:08:58.930 --> 00:08:59.930 line:80%
kill Xiong Qianjin,

00:09:00.410 --> 00:09:01.780 line:80%
and we'll wipe out Xuanwu Altar.

00:09:01.980 --> 00:09:03.050 line:80%
Not me.

00:09:04.690 --> 00:09:05.530 line:80%
You'll do it.

00:09:08.410 --> 00:09:09.250 line:80%
Me?

00:09:09.530 --> 00:09:10.930 line:80%
You'll fight Master Xiong

00:09:10.930 --> 00:09:11.930 line:80%
one-on-one,

00:09:11.930 --> 00:09:13.530 line:80%
fair and square.

00:09:13.530 --> 00:09:14.860 line:80%
If you survive,

00:09:14.860 --> 00:09:16.900 line:80%
then the Xuanwu and Qinglong Altars

00:09:16.900 --> 00:09:19.450 line:80%
will both be under your command.

00:09:22.100 --> 00:09:23.380 line:80%
Young Master,

00:09:23.380 --> 00:09:25.530 line:80%
my skills are lacking.

00:09:25.530 --> 00:09:26.930 line:80%
If I lose by mistake,

00:09:26.930 --> 00:09:28.020 line:80%
my shame is one thing,

00:09:28.020 --> 00:09:28.900 line:80%
but if it dampens

00:09:28.900 --> 00:09:30.620 line:80%
your momentum in reclaiming the sect,

00:09:31.170 --> 00:09:32.050 line:80%
wouldn't that be

00:09:32.410 --> 00:09:33.650 line:80%
an unforgivable sin?

00:09:34.050 --> 00:09:35.930 line:80%
You Guanyue,

00:09:37.330 --> 00:09:39.290 line:80%
you've spent
half your life currying favor,

00:09:39.620 --> 00:09:41.780 line:80%
smiling, and ingratiating yourself.

00:09:42.330 --> 00:09:43.740 line:80%
But that alone isn't enough

00:09:44.220 --> 00:09:45.100 line:80%
to win hearts.

00:09:45.980 --> 00:09:47.530 line:80%
If you want to be an elder

00:09:47.530 --> 00:09:48.443 line:80%
or an enforcer someday,

00:09:49.410 --> 00:09:52.220 line:80%
you'll need to show real skill.

00:09:53.410 --> 00:09:54.250 line:80%
Go.

00:09:54.900 --> 00:09:55.740 line:80%
Kill him.

00:09:57.140 --> 00:09:58.620 line:80%
Consider it your grand opening.

00:10:04.020 --> 00:10:04.860 line:80%
You want me

00:10:05.500 --> 00:10:06.780 line:80%
to fight this piece of trash?

00:10:06.780 --> 00:10:08.290 line:80%
If you can defeat You Guanyue,

00:10:09.020 --> 00:10:10.170 line:80%
I'll spare you today.

00:10:11.330 --> 00:10:12.500 line:80%
You're far too arrogant.

00:10:12.780 --> 00:10:13.740 line:80%
Prepare to die!

00:10:55.930 --> 00:10:56.770 line:80%
You Guanyue,

00:10:57.290 --> 00:10:58.980 line:80%
you'd followed Elder Qiu for years.

00:10:59.500 --> 00:11:01.570 line:80%
He was called the Undying Phoenix,

00:11:02.570 --> 00:11:04.740 line:80%
one who dared to shed his own flesh.

00:11:55.740 --> 00:11:57.450 line:80%
- He won!
- Master You, impressive!

00:11:57.450 --> 00:11:58.650 line:80%
Well done, Master You!

00:12:13.570 --> 00:12:15.450 line:80%
Xiong Qianjin aided evil for years,

00:12:16.290 --> 00:12:17.930 line:80%
slaughtering innocent sect members.

00:12:17.930 --> 00:12:20.740 line:80%
His crimes are countless
and unforgivable.

00:12:20.740 --> 00:12:22.220 line:80%
Killing him today

00:12:22.220 --> 00:12:23.530 line:80%
serves as a warning to all.

00:12:28.530 --> 00:12:31.530 line:80%
As for what comes next,
please enlighten me.

00:12:31.530 --> 00:12:35.050 line:80%
I'll always serve you, Young Master.

00:12:36.170 --> 00:12:39.140 line:80%
We'll always serve you, Young Master.

00:12:39.140 --> 00:12:40.860 line:80%
Flatten Xuanwu Altar.

00:12:42.100 --> 00:12:42.940 line:80%
Kill them!

00:12:44.380 --> 00:12:46.530 line:80%
Charge!

00:12:58.530 --> 00:12:59.530 line:80%
Time is tight.

00:12:59.530 --> 00:13:00.380 line:80%
How do these herbs

00:13:00.780 --> 00:13:02.620 line:80%
counter the Shanci Mushroom poison?

00:13:02.631 --> 00:13:04.111 line:80%
You go back
to Jiuzhou Archive first.

00:13:04.122 --> 00:13:06.034 line:80%
I'll catch a corpse slave
to test the medicine.

00:13:06.045 --> 00:13:06.925 line:80%
- Sure.
- No need.

00:13:07.570 --> 00:13:08.410 line:80%
I'll do it.

00:13:19.500 --> 00:13:20.740 line:80%
When were you poisoned?

00:13:22.900 --> 00:13:24.140 line:80%
No time for this.

00:13:24.140 --> 00:13:25.740 line:80%
Test the medicine first. If it fails,

00:13:25.740 --> 00:13:27.330 line:80%
kill me with one strike.

00:13:27.330 --> 00:13:28.900 line:80%
Then find a place and bury me.

00:13:28.900 --> 00:13:30.226 line:80%
Just take the Sunshine Blade back.

00:13:30.780 --> 00:13:31.780 line:80%
Don't talk nonsense.

00:13:32.170 --> 00:13:33.050 line:80%
It won't come to that.

00:13:55.530 --> 00:13:56.690 line:80%
Why are you so distracted?

00:13:57.170 --> 00:13:58.860 line:80%
I was just thinking about Zhao.

00:13:59.290 --> 00:14:01.170 line:80%
She's been ill for nearly a month now.

00:14:01.570 --> 00:14:02.810 line:80%
I wonder when she'll recover.

00:14:03.140 --> 00:14:04.860 line:80%
She left to find Chang Ning, right?

00:14:05.860 --> 00:14:07.140 line:80%
How do you know?

00:14:07.500 --> 00:14:09.650 line:80%
She took the herbal incense
I prepared for Chang Ning.

00:14:10.330 --> 00:14:11.290 line:80%
That child,

00:14:11.570 --> 00:14:13.020 line:80%
bold and decisive by nature,

00:14:13.810 --> 00:14:14.930 line:80%
is very much like her aunt.

00:14:15.410 --> 00:14:16.500 line:80%
Chang must've gone

00:14:17.140 --> 00:14:18.810 line:80%
to seek revenge against the demon sect.

00:14:20.530 --> 00:14:21.500 line:80%
Uncle Lei,

00:14:21.500 --> 00:14:22.570 line:80%
tell me.

00:14:22.570 --> 00:14:24.860 line:80%
What is this demon sect like?

00:14:24.860 --> 00:14:25.700 line:80%
Is it dangerous?

00:14:26.220 --> 00:14:27.170 line:80%
Is it dangerous?

00:14:31.380 --> 00:14:32.530 line:80%
We'll see

00:14:34.593 --> 00:14:35.580 line:80%
if she comes back intact.

00:15:03.220 --> 00:15:04.060 line:80%
Yu Huiyin.

00:15:20.050 --> 00:15:21.140 line:80%
Corpse slaves.

00:15:21.140 --> 00:15:23.020 line:80%
Nie Zhe is using
corpse slaves against us.

00:15:23.020 --> 00:15:25.140 line:80%
Young Master,
these corpse slaves feel no pain.

00:15:25.140 --> 00:15:26.553 line:80%
They can't be killed; what do we do?

00:15:31.290 --> 00:15:32.130 line:80%
Break!

00:15:34.780 --> 00:15:35.620 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:15:36.570 --> 00:15:39.085 line:80%
you led men to attack my Xuanwu Altar.

00:15:39.096 --> 00:15:40.810 line:80%
Aren't you afraid
the Chief will punish you

00:15:40.810 --> 00:15:42.780 line:80%
and order your execution,

00:15:42.780 --> 00:15:44.140 line:80%
disregarding your families' ties?

00:15:44.140 --> 00:15:45.980 line:80%
Master Shangguan, don't joke.

00:15:45.980 --> 00:15:47.780 line:80%
Nie Zhe is using sect members' lives

00:15:47.780 --> 00:15:49.380 line:80%
to refine corpse slaves.

00:15:49.380 --> 00:15:51.330 line:80%
He's broken a century-old sect rule.

00:15:52.570 --> 00:15:54.290 line:80%
What family ties are left to speak of?

00:15:54.810 --> 00:15:57.330 line:80%
The Chief hasn't touched
a single core member.

00:15:57.650 --> 00:15:59.570 line:80%
He's only used

00:15:59.570 --> 00:16:01.140 line:80%
low-cultivation commoners.

00:16:01.140 --> 00:16:02.330 line:80%
The Chief said

00:16:02.330 --> 00:16:03.380 line:80%
these people

00:16:03.380 --> 00:16:04.650 line:80%
are nothing but vermin.

00:16:04.650 --> 00:16:05.980 line:80%
Even commoners

00:16:05.980 --> 00:16:08.055 line:80%
are loved ones of sect disciples.

00:16:08.066 --> 00:16:09.570 line:80%
How can Nie Zhe trample them at will?

00:16:09.570 --> 00:16:10.410 line:80%
Enough provocation.

00:16:11.380 --> 00:16:13.530 line:80%
You're about to die
and still spout nonsense.

00:16:27.530 --> 00:16:28.740 line:80%
Strike the neck and spine.

00:17:11.610 --> 00:17:12.470 line:80%
Mr. Yu,

00:17:12.500 --> 00:17:13.340 line:80%
I'll assist you.

00:17:21.420 --> 00:17:22.260 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:17:29.940 --> 00:17:31.980 line:80%
I saw something was wrong
with you long ago.

00:17:32.370 --> 00:17:33.220 line:80%
Shangguan Haonan,

00:17:33.660 --> 00:17:35.890 line:80%
you truly are a traitor.

00:17:36.180 --> 00:17:37.020 line:80%
Yu Huiyin,

00:17:37.740 --> 00:17:38.980 line:80%
you aid evil

00:17:39.610 --> 00:17:41.290 line:80%
and slaughter sect members with Nie Zhe.

00:17:41.850 --> 00:17:43.616 line:80%
Once the truth
of the corpse slaves spreads,

00:17:44.323 --> 00:17:46.290 line:80%
let's see who in the sect
will still support you.

00:17:46.740 --> 00:17:47.580 line:80%
Dead men

00:17:48.020 --> 00:17:49.180 line:80%
don't speak.

00:18:42.290 --> 00:18:43.660 line:80%
So, the poison in you

00:18:44.530 --> 00:18:45.890 line:80%
was never fully cured.

00:18:47.700 --> 00:18:48.540 line:80%
Young Master!

00:18:52.660 --> 00:18:53.500 line:80%
Young Master,

00:18:53.976 --> 00:18:55.156 line:80%
I'll carve a path out for you.

00:18:56.330 --> 00:18:57.810 line:80%
Fate has favored me.

00:19:09.570 --> 00:19:10.410 line:80%
Xing...

00:19:24.180 --> 00:19:25.980 line:80%
Young Master, don't hurt her.

00:20:58.850 --> 00:20:59.780 line:80%
Demoness,

00:20:59.780 --> 00:21:00.940 line:80%
you're Cai Pingshu's...

00:21:20.940 --> 00:21:21.780 line:80%
Mu Qingyan!

00:21:30.460 --> 00:21:31.420 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:22:13.890 --> 00:22:14.780 line:80%
You're awake.

00:22:16.330 --> 00:22:17.170 line:80%
Zhao,

00:22:20.090 --> 00:22:21.130 line:80%
you're here.

00:22:34.215 --> 00:22:36.262 line:80%
The herbal incense has been burning
for four hours.

00:22:36.980 --> 00:22:38.290 line:80%
How do you feel?

00:22:42.980 --> 00:22:43.820 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:22:50.220 --> 00:22:52.980 line:80%
Uncle Lei prepared
this herbal incense for you.

00:22:52.980 --> 00:22:54.700 line:80%
It contains dozens of herbs.

00:22:54.700 --> 00:22:57.090 line:80%
It can't eradicate your poison,

00:22:58.020 --> 00:22:59.500 line:80%
but it can suppress it for now.

00:23:01.740 --> 00:23:02.890 line:80%
So, you already know.

00:23:16.890 --> 00:23:17.740 line:80%
You know,

00:23:18.370 --> 00:23:19.570 line:80%
the Li Sect's tailoring craft

00:23:19.570 --> 00:23:20.869 line:80%
is no worse than Granny Needle's.

00:23:22.890 --> 00:23:24.180 line:80%
You look handsome in this outfit.

00:23:24.703 --> 00:23:25.856 line:80%
Like someone from a painting.

00:23:28.810 --> 00:23:30.130 line:80%
So, you're here

00:23:30.890 --> 00:23:32.850 line:80%
to pity a dying man like me?

00:23:35.500 --> 00:23:36.570 line:80%
Everyone dies.

00:23:37.090 --> 00:23:39.420 line:80%
Some die sooner;

00:23:39.660 --> 00:23:40.570 line:80%
some die later.

00:23:40.980 --> 00:23:42.370 line:80%
There is nothing strange about it.

00:23:42.740 --> 00:23:44.020 line:80%
Why would I pity you?

00:23:44.940 --> 00:23:46.220 line:80%
Ever since I can remember,

00:23:46.740 --> 00:23:48.530 line:80%
I knew my aunt was nearing the end.

00:23:50.290 --> 00:23:51.460 line:80%
But I never felt

00:23:52.370 --> 00:23:53.660 line:80%
she needed anyone's pity.

00:23:54.460 --> 00:23:56.020 line:80%
The day before she passed,

00:23:56.020 --> 00:23:57.660 line:80%
she even made Smiley with me.

00:23:58.780 --> 00:24:01.090 line:80%
It was fragrant and sweet that day.

00:24:02.020 --> 00:24:02.860 line:80%
She said

00:24:03.850 --> 00:24:05.376 line:80%
her wishes in this life were fulfilled.

00:24:05.610 --> 00:24:06.660 line:80%
Even if she died,

00:24:07.090 --> 00:24:08.129 line:80%
she would have no regrets.

00:24:10.780 --> 00:24:12.020 line:80%
So, are you here

00:24:13.180 --> 00:24:14.420 line:80%
to help me fulfill my wish?

00:24:14.890 --> 00:24:16.890 line:80%
I'll use every possible way to save you.

00:24:16.890 --> 00:24:18.180 line:80%
If I cannot save you,

00:24:18.180 --> 00:24:19.180 line:80%
I will help you

00:24:19.180 --> 00:24:20.290 line:80%
fulfill your wish.

00:24:20.610 --> 00:24:21.940 line:80%
If you want revenge,

00:24:22.620 --> 00:24:23.780 line:80%
I will help you take revenge.

00:24:24.420 --> 00:24:25.460 line:80%
What then?

00:24:25.980 --> 00:24:26.820 line:80%
Then?

00:24:29.180 --> 00:24:31.370 line:80%
I'll go back to Qingque sect with Yuzhi?

00:24:45.330 --> 00:24:46.170 line:80%
Don't leave.

00:24:47.660 --> 00:24:49.130 line:80%
Okay, I won't.

00:24:51.050 --> 00:24:52.220 line:80%
All right.

00:24:52.700 --> 00:24:54.246 line:80%
I'll leave after I finish things, okay?

00:25:00.740 --> 00:25:02.050 line:80%
Zhao, this is...

00:25:02.050 --> 00:25:03.180 line:80%
People slip up sometimes.

00:25:03.180 --> 00:25:04.220 line:80%
Horses stumble too.

00:25:04.220 --> 00:25:05.780 line:80%
It just happened by accident.

00:25:05.780 --> 00:25:06.980 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:25:06.980 --> 00:25:08.810 line:80%
I've found herbs to suppress the poison.

00:25:09.180 --> 00:25:10.940 line:80%
If the Gu worms aren't cleared in time,

00:25:12.180 --> 00:25:13.330 line:80%
they'll erode your mind.

00:25:14.053 --> 00:25:16.079 line:80%
You'll lose your senses and die.
Do you know that?

00:25:25.180 --> 00:25:26.040 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:25:26.050 --> 00:25:27.400 line:80%
We've only been apart for days,

00:25:28.360 --> 00:25:30.096 line:80%
and you've turned yourself
into this state.

00:25:31.570 --> 00:25:32.410 line:80%
It's fine.

00:25:32.570 --> 00:25:33.503 line:80%
The fortune teller said

00:25:33.700 --> 00:25:34.810 line:80%
I'd live a long life.

00:25:35.436 --> 00:25:36.370 line:80%
I don't believe in fate.

00:25:37.370 --> 00:25:38.530 line:80%
I only believe in myself.

00:25:40.180 --> 00:25:41.290 line:80%
What are you trying to do?

00:25:42.957 --> 00:25:45.023 line:80%
Thankfully, we have the medicine
Miss Feng brought.

00:25:45.740 --> 00:25:47.290 line:80%
Xing should wake up soon.

00:25:48.050 --> 00:25:48.890 line:80%
Be gentle.

00:25:51.020 --> 00:25:52.420 line:80%
I'm performing acupuncture on Xing.

00:25:52.940 --> 00:25:54.890 line:80%
Why do you hurt more than she does?

00:25:57.850 --> 00:25:59.330 line:80%
Xing, forgive me.

00:26:04.740 --> 00:26:05.766 line:80%
You're so clumsy.

00:26:05.777 --> 00:26:06.717 line:80%
You're driving me crazy.

00:26:08.079 --> 00:26:09.209 line:80%
Why don't you do it yourself?

00:26:09.850 --> 00:26:11.020 line:80%
If I weren't injured,

00:26:11.420 --> 00:26:12.420 line:80%
would I need you?

00:26:13.740 --> 00:26:15.660 line:80%
A fence-sitter
who only knows how to talk.

00:26:15.660 --> 00:26:16.500 line:80%
I...

00:26:17.980 --> 00:26:19.420 line:80%
At least I'm not like you,

00:26:19.420 --> 00:26:20.976 line:80%
living off flattery toward Nie Zhe,

00:26:20.987 --> 00:26:22.632 line:80%
holding a post without doing any work.

00:26:22.643 --> 00:26:23.660 line:80%
Who are you talking about?

00:26:23.660 --> 00:26:24.993 line:80%
Whoever gets angry is who I mean.

00:26:25.280 --> 00:26:26.220 line:80%
Are you feeling guilty?

00:26:26.220 --> 00:26:27.130 line:80%
You Guanyue.

00:26:32.250 --> 00:26:33.100 line:80%
Xing.

00:26:33.130 --> 00:26:33.970 line:80%
Xing.

00:26:35.810 --> 00:26:37.810 line:80%
So naggy that my ears hurt.

00:26:38.530 --> 00:26:39.370 line:80%
Go away.

00:26:40.420 --> 00:26:41.570 line:80%
Do you feel unwell?

00:26:43.740 --> 00:26:44.780 line:80%
Take me to Miss Feng.

00:26:49.420 --> 00:26:50.260 line:80%
Xing.

00:26:53.780 --> 00:26:55.220 line:80%
- Xing.
- Xing.

00:26:55.220 --> 00:26:56.060 line:80%
Xing.

00:27:00.180 --> 00:27:01.020 line:80%
Mr. Dai.

00:27:03.050 --> 00:27:05.700 line:80%
Thanks to you and Miss Feng
for saving my life.

00:27:05.700 --> 00:27:08.130 line:80%
It seems the Gu poison in you has eased.

00:27:09.020 --> 00:27:10.290 line:80%
My Xing is fine.

00:27:10.610 --> 00:27:12.530 line:80%
No need for you to worry.

00:27:12.810 --> 00:27:13.650 line:80%
That's good then.

00:27:13.970 --> 00:27:15.043 line:80%
I came to look for Xiaohan.

00:27:15.420 --> 00:27:16.420 line:80%
What a coincidence.

00:27:16.420 --> 00:27:17.656 line:80%
We're also here for Miss Feng.

00:27:17.667 --> 00:27:19.700 line:80%
She and the Young Master
spent the night together.

00:27:19.700 --> 00:27:20.890 line:80%
They must be

00:27:20.890 --> 00:27:22.530 line:80%
deeply in love

00:27:22.530 --> 00:27:24.020 line:80%
and inseparable now.

00:27:24.020 --> 00:27:24.860 line:80%
Get lost.

00:27:26.050 --> 00:27:26.890 line:80%
Zhao...

00:27:28.660 --> 00:27:30.940 line:80%
Your valor conquered Xuanwu Altar.

00:27:30.940 --> 00:27:33.130 line:80%
Xing and I came to offer
congratulations and thanks.

00:27:35.980 --> 00:27:37.890 line:80%
Did you argue with Xiaohan?

00:27:39.530 --> 00:27:41.780 line:80%
I wanted to take Zhao's pulse
and examine her,

00:27:41.780 --> 00:27:42.980 line:80%
but she refused.

00:27:43.370 --> 00:27:44.210 line:80%
Examine her...

00:27:45.610 --> 00:27:46.450 line:80%
Examine her?

00:27:46.940 --> 00:27:47.780 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:27:48.460 --> 00:27:49.780 line:80%
is there a way to fully eradicate

00:27:49.780 --> 00:27:50.793 line:80%
the Gu poison in Xiaohan?

00:27:51.530 --> 00:27:52.610 line:80%
Yan Xu fears Nie Zhe,

00:27:53.086 --> 00:27:54.566 line:80%
so he must be holding something back.

00:27:55.050 --> 00:27:57.180 line:80%
I'll go to Jiuzhou Archive now

00:27:57.470 --> 00:27:58.410 line:80%
to find Yan Xu.

00:28:02.050 --> 00:28:02.940 line:80%
We just settled here.

00:28:02.940 --> 00:28:04.169 line:80%
There's much work awaiting you.

00:28:04.410 --> 00:28:05.149 line:80%
Besides,

00:28:05.160 --> 00:28:07.246 line:80%
you've fought several rounds
with unhealed injuries.

00:28:07.810 --> 00:28:08.650 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:28:09.610 --> 00:28:10.450 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:28:10.533 --> 00:28:11.540 line:80%
let me go find Elder Yan.

00:28:12.020 --> 00:28:12.980 line:80%
You stay here.

00:28:12.980 --> 00:28:14.130 line:80%
If Nie Zhe counterattacks,

00:28:14.130 --> 00:28:14.970 line:80%
you'll be ready.

00:28:23.420 --> 00:28:24.260 line:80%
Senior,

00:28:24.460 --> 00:28:25.610 line:80%
do you feel any better today?

00:28:27.370 --> 00:28:28.890 line:80%
Same as always.

00:28:29.420 --> 00:28:31.130 line:80%
Just barely hanging on.

00:28:32.220 --> 00:28:33.060 line:80%
Senior,

00:28:33.980 --> 00:28:35.610 line:80%
Mu Qingyan is advancing aggressively.

00:28:36.700 --> 00:28:37.810 line:80%
In a few days,

00:28:38.330 --> 00:28:40.050 line:80%
he'll likely attack Bliss Palace.

00:28:40.050 --> 00:28:41.530 line:80%
You useless thing.

00:28:41.530 --> 00:28:44.780 line:80%
You've ruled the sect for over ten years
on your uncle's behalf,

00:28:44.780 --> 00:28:48.500 line:80%
yet now you're being beaten
by that Mu brat.

00:28:48.500 --> 00:28:50.700 line:80%
If not for Shangguan's betrayal

00:28:51.610 --> 00:28:53.530 line:80%
and Yu Huiyin and Fengge's injuries,

00:28:54.396 --> 00:28:56.000 line:80%
how would I have fallen into this state?

00:28:56.500 --> 00:28:57.340 line:80%
Senior,

00:28:58.290 --> 00:28:59.660 line:80%
please give me some guidance.

00:29:01.740 --> 00:29:03.810 line:80%
You wouldn't just watch Uncle's legacy

00:29:03.810 --> 00:29:04.770 line:80%
be destroyed, would you?

00:29:09.500 --> 00:29:12.890 line:80%
If my legs hadn't been crippled
by Cai Pingshu,

00:29:12.890 --> 00:29:14.330 line:80%
how would it come to this?

00:29:15.020 --> 00:29:15.860 line:80%
Very well.

00:29:16.500 --> 00:29:18.940 line:80%
Lure that Mu brat here.

00:29:18.940 --> 00:29:21.980 line:80%
I'll eliminate this threat to the sect.

00:29:24.130 --> 00:29:24.970 line:80%
Shangguan,

00:29:25.290 --> 00:29:26.700 line:80%
you traitorous wretch.

00:29:27.090 --> 00:29:28.530 line:80%
The Chief trusted you so deeply,

00:29:28.980 --> 00:29:30.130 line:80%
yet you betrayed him.

00:29:30.660 --> 00:29:32.010 line:80%
How fickle

00:29:32.290 --> 00:29:33.460 line:80%
and ungrateful.

00:29:34.020 --> 00:29:35.130 line:80%
The Young Master arrives.

00:29:43.610 --> 00:29:44.450 line:80%
Young Master,

00:29:44.660 --> 00:29:46.180 line:80%
all forces of Xuanwu Altar are here,

00:29:46.500 --> 00:29:47.460 line:80%
awaiting your judgment.

00:29:50.740 --> 00:29:52.290 line:80%
Crooked mouth and slanted eyes.

00:29:52.290 --> 00:29:53.130 line:80%
Kill him.

00:29:54.290 --> 00:29:55.290 line:80%
- Go.
- Let me go.

00:29:55.290 --> 00:29:56.290 line:80%
Let me go.

00:29:59.700 --> 00:30:00.890 line:80%
Shifty-eyed and sneaky.

00:30:01.530 --> 00:30:02.370 line:80%
Kill him.

00:30:02.660 --> 00:30:03.500 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:30:03.850 --> 00:30:05.810 line:80%
- Let me go.
- Two-faced turncoat.

00:30:06.180 --> 00:30:07.020 line:80%
Kill him.

00:30:07.031 --> 00:30:07.771 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:30:07.782 --> 00:30:08.810 line:80%
- Go.
- No more nonsense.

00:30:08.810 --> 00:30:10.050 line:80%
He can't tell grain from millet.

00:30:10.050 --> 00:30:10.980 line:80%
Kill him.

00:30:10.980 --> 00:30:12.700 line:80%
Lazy and useless.

00:30:12.700 --> 00:30:13.540 line:80%
Kill him.

00:30:13.620 --> 00:30:14.490 line:80%
Young Master.

00:30:14.610 --> 00:30:15.570 line:80%
Spare my life.

00:30:15.570 --> 00:30:16.700 line:80%
Talkative

00:30:16.700 --> 00:30:18.050 line:80%
and meddlesome.

00:30:18.700 --> 00:30:19.540 line:80%
Kill them all.

00:30:21.740 --> 00:30:22.940 line:80%
- Spare me.
- Spare me.

00:30:23.660 --> 00:30:24.980 line:80%
We're willing to surrender.

00:30:24.980 --> 00:30:26.500 line:80%
Young Master, spare us.

00:30:26.500 --> 00:30:28.020 line:80%
Please, spare us.

00:30:28.020 --> 00:30:30.090 line:80%
Get up.

00:30:30.940 --> 00:30:32.370 line:80%
Go.

00:30:32.370 --> 00:30:33.940 line:80%
Are you really going to kill them all?

00:30:37.500 --> 00:30:38.780 line:80%
They're nothing but people

00:30:38.780 --> 00:30:40.220 line:80%
who repeatedly broke sect rules

00:30:40.220 --> 00:30:41.610 line:80%
and are drenched in blood.

00:30:42.780 --> 00:30:43.620 line:80%
Why not?

00:30:44.020 --> 00:30:46.180 line:80%
But such a large Xuanwu Altar

00:30:46.180 --> 00:30:47.130 line:80%
still needs people

00:30:47.130 --> 00:30:48.460 line:80%
to handle odds and ends.

00:30:48.980 --> 00:30:50.290 line:80%
It might be better to keep a few.

00:30:50.940 --> 00:30:52.370 line:80%
They're all top-tier fighters.

00:30:52.940 --> 00:30:55.500 line:80%
They'd cause grudges between us
and those they once persecuted,

00:30:56.330 --> 00:30:58.020 line:80%
or even waver and secretly collude

00:30:58.570 --> 00:31:01.050 line:80%
with Nie Zhe.

00:31:02.370 --> 00:31:03.570 line:80%
Before yesterday's battle,

00:31:04.130 --> 00:31:05.570 line:80%
the Young Master ordered me

00:31:05.570 --> 00:31:07.420 line:80%
to leave a corner open in the northeast

00:31:07.940 --> 00:31:10.130 line:80%
so the weak-willed could escape.

00:31:10.130 --> 00:31:11.500 line:80%
Those who stayed to resist

00:31:12.420 --> 00:31:13.740 line:80%
are all utterly loyal

00:31:13.740 --> 00:31:14.893 line:80%
to Nie Zhe and Xiong Qianjin.

00:31:15.290 --> 00:31:16.130 line:80%
What use are they?

00:31:17.530 --> 00:31:19.220 line:80%
So, you've filtered them out.

00:31:19.780 --> 00:31:21.940 line:80%
I was short-sighted.

00:31:21.940 --> 00:31:23.570 line:80%
You and Shangguan are both soft-hearted.

00:31:24.530 --> 00:31:25.530 line:80%
Handing them to you

00:31:26.020 --> 00:31:27.090 line:80%
would inevitably be a risk.

00:31:27.890 --> 00:31:30.290 line:80%
All these years, you dealt cautiously

00:31:30.639 --> 00:31:31.766 line:80%
with Nie Zhe and his faction.

00:31:33.290 --> 00:31:34.460 line:80%
Thanks for your efforts.

00:31:36.780 --> 00:31:37.620 line:80%
From now on,

00:31:39.130 --> 00:31:41.700 line:80%
I'll return to you
a clean and pure sect.

00:31:46.180 --> 00:31:47.810 line:80%
Ever since you were injured by Nie Zhe

00:31:47.810 --> 00:31:48.650 line:80%
and went missing,

00:31:49.050 --> 00:31:50.570 line:80%
I nearly failed endure.

00:31:51.980 --> 00:31:53.570 line:80%
I always remembered your kindness

00:31:53.570 --> 00:31:55.090 line:80%
and found ways
to maneuver among them.

00:31:55.460 --> 00:31:57.330 line:80%
But watching them harm sect members

00:31:57.330 --> 00:31:58.780 line:80%
was truly tormenting.

00:31:58.780 --> 00:31:59.620 line:80%
Nie kept

00:32:00.740 --> 00:32:02.460 line:80%
probing and testing me.

00:32:03.940 --> 00:32:05.420 line:80%
Life was unbearable.

00:32:06.050 --> 00:32:08.530 line:80%
Dealing with that suspicious rat?

00:32:10.020 --> 00:32:10.860 line:80%
Shangguan,

00:32:11.370 --> 00:32:12.570 line:80%
it hasn't been easy for you.

00:32:17.710 --> 00:32:18.660 line:80%
You did very well.

00:32:20.290 --> 00:32:21.790 line:80%
I had you investigate something.

00:32:22.090 --> 00:32:22.930 line:80%
What did you find?

00:32:23.423 --> 00:32:24.940 line:80%
When I was young in the Demonic Camp,

00:32:25.780 --> 00:32:27.530 line:80%
I once saw Elder Tianji Duan Jiuxiu

00:32:27.530 --> 00:32:29.056 line:80%
use the Wudu Palm to kill for practice.

00:32:29.610 --> 00:32:30.576 line:80%
But from my observation,

00:32:31.050 --> 00:32:31.940 line:80%
what Nie Zhe practices

00:32:32.500 --> 00:32:33.980 line:80%
has the moves but lacks inner force.

00:32:34.370 --> 00:32:35.986 line:80%
He hasn't truly mastered the Wudu Palm.

00:32:36.290 --> 00:32:37.370 line:80%
(It's not the Wudu Palm?)

00:32:38.570 --> 00:32:40.220 line:80%
(Then what is the poison in my body?)

00:32:43.420 --> 00:32:44.260 line:80%
Young Master,

00:32:44.660 --> 00:32:46.570 line:80%
Mr. Dai has brought Elder Yan Xu.

00:32:54.530 --> 00:32:55.370 line:80%
I don't know.

00:32:56.090 --> 00:32:58.330 line:80%
And even if I did, I wouldn't tell you.

00:32:58.330 --> 00:32:59.330 line:80%
Stop bothering with that.

00:32:59.330 --> 00:33:00.290 line:80%
Hurry and send me back.

00:33:02.090 --> 00:33:03.570 line:80%
If you refuse to speak,

00:33:04.500 --> 00:33:05.660 line:80%
I can only tell Nie Zhe

00:33:06.370 --> 00:33:07.830 line:80%
that when I fled the sect back then,

00:33:08.370 --> 00:33:09.740 line:80%
it was you who helped me.

00:33:09.740 --> 00:33:10.740 line:80%
You...

00:33:10.740 --> 00:33:12.700 line:80%
If you're willing to share something,

00:33:13.420 --> 00:33:14.260 line:80%
I guarantee

00:33:14.570 --> 00:33:16.330 line:80%
that before I take over Bliss Palace,

00:33:16.810 --> 00:33:18.890 line:80%
I never once met you.

00:33:20.660 --> 00:33:21.980 line:80%
Excellent.

00:33:22.610 --> 00:33:25.090 line:80%
When you take Bliss Palace,

00:33:25.090 --> 00:33:27.130 line:80%
I'll personally congratulate you.

00:33:29.610 --> 00:33:30.820 line:80%
I've never seen a fence-sitter

00:33:30.830 --> 00:33:32.330 line:80%
be so fresh and shameless.

00:33:33.850 --> 00:33:35.285 line:80%
You little brat.

00:33:35.296 --> 00:33:37.050 line:80%
(Qinglong Altar)
I've said it several times.

00:33:37.050 --> 00:33:38.530 line:80%
You dragged me here for no reason

00:33:38.530 --> 00:33:40.980 line:80%
just to ask
about this Gu-clearing method.

00:33:40.980 --> 00:33:42.530 line:80%
I truly haven't seen it.

00:33:43.130 --> 00:33:44.700 line:80%
How many times do you want to ask?

00:33:45.020 --> 00:33:46.530 line:80%
Corpse slaves first appeared

00:33:46.660 --> 00:33:48.180 line:80%
19 years ago, in early spring.

00:33:49.020 --> 00:33:51.660 line:80%
You know
the former chief's movements best.

00:33:52.410 --> 00:33:54.030 line:80%
Do you recall whether Nie Hengcheng

00:33:54.087 --> 00:33:55.293 line:80%
visited any special place then?

00:33:57.800 --> 00:33:59.290 line:80%
This matter...

00:34:00.370 --> 00:34:01.570 line:80%
I think I remember.

00:34:01.850 --> 00:34:03.180 line:80%
That March,

00:34:03.780 --> 00:34:06.370 line:80%
the former leader often went
near the Youming Path.

00:34:06.370 --> 00:34:07.850 line:80%
There was a herbal garden inside.

00:34:07.850 --> 00:34:10.010 line:80%
Every time he went there,

00:34:10.010 --> 00:34:12.410 line:80%
he'd stay for quite a while.

00:34:13.426 --> 00:34:14.559 line:80%
Where is this herbal garden?

00:34:18.780 --> 00:34:20.450 line:80%
It's a secret realm of the Nie clan.

00:34:20.450 --> 00:34:22.180 line:80%
Outsiders don't know.

00:34:26.810 --> 00:34:28.290 line:80%
The Youming Path...

00:34:29.290 --> 00:34:31.060 line:80%
Lady Sun, it's so late.

00:34:31.060 --> 00:34:33.140 line:80%
Why are you in such a remote place?

00:34:33.140 --> 00:34:34.326 line:80%
Picking flowers for the Chief.

00:34:34.890 --> 00:34:37.450 line:80%
These flowers must have night dew

00:34:37.450 --> 00:34:38.930 line:80%
to be effective.

00:34:38.930 --> 00:34:40.850 line:80%
(Is the place
where Lady Sun picked flowers)

00:34:40.850 --> 00:34:42.180 line:80%
(the herbal garden?)

00:34:42.180 --> 00:34:43.580 line:80%
I know a place.

00:34:43.580 --> 00:34:44.930 line:80%
The herbal garden might be there.

00:34:45.350 --> 00:34:46.220 line:80%
I'll go with you.

00:34:46.220 --> 00:34:47.060 line:80%
Let's go.

00:34:47.970 --> 00:34:48.810 line:80%
Don't go.

00:34:49.140 --> 00:34:50.453 line:80%
I've prepared a decoction for you

00:34:50.640 --> 00:34:52.173 line:80%
to suppress the Gu poison in your body.

00:34:52.450 --> 00:34:53.290 line:80%
Mr. Dai,

00:34:54.330 --> 00:34:55.220 line:80%
may we talk privately?

00:35:03.121 --> 00:35:13.781 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:35:32.541 --> 00:35:36.951 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:35:37.516 --> 00:35:42.131 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:35:42.471 --> 00:35:47.036 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:35:47.561 --> 00:35:51.861 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:35:54.806 --> 00:35:59.506 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:36:00.031 --> 00:36:04.321 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:36:04.981 --> 00:36:09.011 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:36:09.326 --> 00:36:14.451 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:36:15.026 --> 00:36:19.836 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:36:20.051 --> 00:36:24.221 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:36:24.946 --> 00:36:28.881 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:36:29.381 --> 00:36:34.656 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:36:57.386 --> 00:37:02.516 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:37:02.881 --> 00:37:07.251 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:37:07.516 --> 00:37:11.646 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:37:11.831 --> 00:37:17.406 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪